很重要的。极星<ins><a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/polestar-will-join-volvo-in-switching-to-teslas-ev-charging-standard-144653065.html">刚刚宣布实施</a></ins>连接器的数量，以及<ins><a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/volvo-is-the-latest-automaker-to-adopt-teslas-ev-charging-standard-191942675.html">沃尔沃也做了同样的事</a></ins>移动。<ins> <a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/ford-ev-drivers-will-get-access-to-12000-north-american-tesla-superchargers-next-spring-221752191.html">福特</a></ins>,<ins> <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/gm-ev-owners-will-gain-access-to-tesla-superchargers-in-2024-002123436.html">通用汽车</a></ins>和<ins><a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/rivian-owners-will-be-able-to-use-tesla-superchargers-starting-in-2024-141546633.html">里维安</a></ins>还承诺在北美使用特斯拉的技术。汽车行业最重要的标准化机构之一国际汽车工程师学会 (SAE International) 最近宣布<ins><a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-sae-is-creating-a-standardized-version-of-teslas-ev-charging-plug-175233691.html">它对插头的支持，</a></ins>正式使 NACS 连接器成为城里最大的游戏。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/electrify-americas-charging-network-will-support-teslas-nacs-connector-by-2025-185317197.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/electrify-americas-charging-network-will-support-teslas-nacs-connector-by-2025-185317197.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 5ebbfb99-60f9-47ce-8b0e-ef8001c68aa4</guid><dc:creator>劳伦斯·邦克</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Thu, 29 Jun 2023 18:53:17 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1688064798</ingested><modified> 2023-06-29T18:53:21+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Automotive Industry]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA